WEBVTT

00:00:01.649 --> 00:00:10.650
Where can you find help to deal with the pressures and stress that come as you grow up?

00:00:10.650 --> 00:00:16.730
Millions of people will give advice on just about anything.

00:00:16.730 --> 00:00:34.270
But how do you sift through all the noise and find advice that really works with no hidden agenda?

00:00:34.270 --> 00:00:39.829
Enter the Bible!

00:00:42.140 --> 00:00:48.609
Wait a second, isn't the Bible like thousands of years old?

00:00:48.609 --> 00:00:53.609
It is, but it s filled with our creator s timeless wisdom.

00:00:53.609 --> 00:01:00.609
The Bible has principles or fundamental truths that help you make good decisions and work through problems.

00:01:00.609 --> 00:01:05.609
It also introduces you to people who dealt with issues similar to yours.

00:01:05.609 --> 00:01:08.609
Is it hard for you to make true friends?

00:01:09.609 --> 00:01:15.609
Consider Ruth a woman in the Bible account who was an excellent example of a selfless empathetic friend.

00:01:15.609 --> 00:01:21.609
Although Ruth and her friend Naomi were very different people in age and culture,

00:01:21.609 --> 00:01:24.609
Ruth stuck with her friend during difficult times.

00:01:24.609 --> 00:01:28.609
She looked out for her and really cared about her feelings.

00:01:28.609 --> 00:01:35.609
Ruth is just one of the many real people in the Bible who overcame real problems.

00:01:36.609 --> 00:01:38.609
Do you struggle to get along with your family?

00:01:38.609 --> 00:01:46.560
Read about Jacob to learn how to deal with disagreements and make peace.

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:49.560
Are you being pressured to have sex?

00:01:49.560 --> 00:01:57.129
Learn why Joseph stood up for himself and how he resisted the pressure.

00:01:57.129 --> 00:02:00.129
Isaiah 48-17 says,

00:02:00.129 --> 00:02:06.129
I, Jehovah, am your God, the one teaching you to benefit yourself.

00:02:06.129 --> 00:02:14.939
God packed the Bible full of practical advice to help us in today s hectic world.

00:02:14.939 --> 00:02:16.939
So why not check it out for yourself?

00:02:16.939 --> 00:02:25.939
Read the Bible on jw.org or in print and learn how the Bible can help you live your best life possible.
